    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>onion</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>ginger</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>chopped chilli</strong>, <strong>curry powder </strong>and<strong> chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to a <strong>food processor </strong></p><p>Blitz until smooth or very finely chopped – this is your <strong>spicy madras paste</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
