      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>spicy madras paste </strong>and the <strong>tomato wedges</strong> to the chicken and cook for 3-4 min further</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>in 200ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [350ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and stir in the <strong>tomato paste</strong> – this is your<strong> tomato stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
