        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>tomato stock</strong> to the pan and cook for 10 min further or until the sauce has thickened and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Roughly chop the <strong>coriander</strong>, including the stalks</p><p>Add <strong>half </strong>of the <strong>chopped coriander</strong> to the sauce (save some for garnish!) and stir it all together – this is your <strong>spicy chicken madras</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
