    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spicy chicken madras </strong>over the<strong> basmati rice </strong>and dollop<strong> </strong>the <strong>cooling</strong> <strong>raita </strong>on top</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
